namecoin (P2P distributed naming system)

Namecoin is a distributed naming system based on bitcoin
technology (a cryptocurrency). 

* Securely record and transfer arbitrary names (keys).
* Attach a value (data) to the names (up to 520 bytes, more in the future). 
* Transact namecoins, the digital currency (NMC).

Project Website: https://namecoin.info
